00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:14.000
 [Bodhi Chata]

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:20.000
 Okay, so this morning I'm going to talk about bodhichitta.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:31.000
 As you all know, this month is a very special month according to the Tibetan Buddhist Calendar.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:37.000
 When the great teacher Bodhisattvatmani reached enlightenment,

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:45.690
 he continued to earn the will of Dharma that brings joy and peace, harmony, and equality to all the

00:00:45.690 --> 00:00:47.000
 living beings.

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:53.240
 But then in the middle of his life, with the consequences of many different other kinds of

00:00:53.240 --> 00:00:54.000
 situations,

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:59.000
 then the Buddha did these miracle activities.

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:03.000
 This is not just that he wants to do these miracle activities,

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:10.830
 but the circumstances and consequences brought up, that is in a way pushed to do these miracle

00:01:10.830 --> 00:01:12.000
 activities.

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:19.000
 And that must be also all, it's just kind of dynamic displays that happen, then happening,

00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:28.000
 in order to glorify the magnificent and beautiful, the peaceful, authentic gauntlet of the Buddha,

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:35.000
 then he did demonstrate these miracle activities with the, in a way, different contexts.

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:42.500
 So then, this is known as miracle activities. Buddha performed these miracle activities from day

00:01:42.500 --> 00:01:44.000
 one of the lunar calendar,

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:52.000
 about 15 days ago, and he continued to perform these until today.

00:01:52.000 --> 00:02:02.530
 Today is the according calendar, or the Buddhist account is the final days of that beautiful

00:02:02.530 --> 00:02:03.000
 display that Buddha performed.

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:10.230
 In that time, so many gathered, so many purposes gathered, the devotees gathered, the choristers

00:02:10.230 --> 00:02:11.000
 gathered,

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:15.000
 and all just a general kind of interesting person gathered.

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:20.000
 Over hundreds and hundreds of thousands came in the shavastha and then displayed.

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:27.250
 So, today is ever since in the Buddhist, in the very Buddhism, considering this one of the very

00:02:27.250 --> 00:02:28.000
 special month,

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:33.000
 that brings a lot of good energy, of the positive energy, virtuous energy.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:40.000
 And there's a kind of big currents moving in the time zone, that very beautiful spiritual energy.

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:46.000
 Every kind of ride on that, in a way, this is what's called a big kind of surfing days.

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:56.000
 Every ride on that surfing boat, we really can, kind of, erecting or evaluating beautiful energy

00:02:56.000 --> 00:02:57.000
 and beautiful realization.

00:02:57.000 --> 00:03:00.000
 And therefore, it is also known as a multiplying month.

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:07.000
 And one, very truly activities transformed and multiplied over a hundred thousand times.

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:10.000
 That's what the teaching said. So, this is very special day.

